<title>UK: UBS sets warrants on Nestle shares.</title>
<headline>UBS sets warrants on Nestle shares.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Union Bank of Switzerland, Zurich said it has issued 40 million American-style call warrants, on Nestle registered shares.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 100 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    2100 CHF		  PREMIUM	18.9 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     1.30 CHF		  GEARING	14.49 X</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	19.MAR.99		 PAYDATE	02.JUL.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS EXCHANGE	  MIN EXER LOT 100</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  1875 CHF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
</text>
